    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, ideal for a buyer looking for a reliable commute rather than a showpiece. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood and roof, though the body remains structurally sound. Inside, the cabin shows signs of regular use with some wear on the driver's seat and minor carpet staining. Mechanically, it starts and runs well, having been serviced regularly to ensure it stays dependable on the road.",
