    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing a rare find for any serious buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine and absolutely no scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the leather and upholstery are pristine, showing zero signs of wear and still retaining that new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a full service history and every component functioning exactly as intended. This is a collector-grade example that offers a like-new driving experience.",
